Package: datacomb
Title: Visual Analysis Tool for Tabular Data
Version: 1.0.0
Description:
    Allows for visually combing through datasets with
    filter, sort, and groupBy functions. The interface can also
    be expanded to show histograms, scatter plots, and
    summary statistics by column.
